  {
   "default": "0",
   "depends_on": "eval:doc.enable_accounting_integration",
   "description": "When enabled, each submitted Night Audit posts room revenue as a Journal Entry (Dr receivable gross per stay, Cr room revenue net, and one Cr per tax account from the stay's Rate Type Tax Schedule). Checkout Sales Invoices then skip Room Charge lines so revenue is not booked twice. Requires ERPXpand and night audits completed for all stay nights before checkout.",
